 <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 italic">Wireless charging is no longer just about convenience; it's about heat management and protocol alignment. With the rise of Qi2 and MagSafe, choosing the right manufacturing partner is critical to avoiding high return rates. At WOWOHCOOL, we prioritize coil alignment and thermal safety above all.</p>
