 </svg>WOWOHCOOL Solution</h3>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Our wireless charger solutions use <strong>NP0 capacitors</strong> to ensure stable FOD detection even under high-temperature conditions. This premium component prevents false triggers and ensures safety compliance.</p>
 </div>
