 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">6. Why Source Wireless Chargers from China?</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">China remains the world's manufacturing hub for consumer electronics, and wireless chargers are no exception. Here's why B2B buyers choose Chinese factories:</p>
 
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
