 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">14. Sample Evaluation Process</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Before committing to bulk orders, evaluate samples systematically. This sample evaluation process helps you make data-driven decisions:</p>
 
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
 <h4 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-6">Sample Evaluation Timeline</h4>
 <div class="space-y-4">
 <div class="flex gap-4">
 <div class="w-20 text-right font-black text-brandOrange">Day 1-3</div>
 <div>
 <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Request Multiple Samples</h5>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Request samples from 3-5 factories simultaneously. Specify exact requirements including charging speed, materials, and certifications needed.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="flex gap-4">
 <div class="w-20 text-right font-black text-brandOrange">Day 4-10</div>
 <div>
 <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Physical Inspection</h5>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Check build quality, finish, weight, and alignment. Test all charging positions and verify LED indicators function correctly.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="flex gap-4">
 <div class="w-20 text-right font-black text-brandOrange">Day 11-14</div>
 <div>
 <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Performance Testing</h5>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Test charging efficiency using professional equipment. Check heat generation during extended charging sessions and verify Qi compatibility.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 <div class="flex gap-4">
 <div class="w-20 text-right font-black text-brandOrange">Day 15-21</div>
 <div>
 <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Certification Verification</h5>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Verify certificates directly with issuing bodies. Request test reports and cross-reference with factory claims.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

