 <section id="payment-terms" class="mb-16">
 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">16. Payment Terms & Trade Assurance</h2>
 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Understanding payment terms protects both parties. Here's what B2B buyers should know:</p>

 <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
 <div class="overflow-x-auto">
 <table class="w-full border border-slate-200 rounded-xl">
 <thead class="bg-slate-100">
 <tr>
 <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Payment Method</th>
 <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Pros</th>
 <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Cons</th>
 <th class="text-left p-4 font-black text-slate-900 uppercase text-sm">Best For</th>
 </tr>
 </thead>
 <tbody>
 <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
 <td class="p-4 font-bold text-slate-900">T/T (Wire Transfer)</td>
 <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">Low fees, fast, widely accepted</td>
 <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">No buyer protection</td>
 <td class="p-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">Established relationships</td>
 </tr>
 <tr class="border-t border-slate-200">
 <td class="p-4 font-bold text-slate-900">L/C (Letter of Credit)</td>
